snippet.textDisplay: Papon gets more respect from me because he tries to bring Assamese traditional and folk songs to national stage. Arijit, Kumar Shanu, Abhijeet, none did this. They come/came to bengal to sing bengali songs, but that's it.
snippet.textOriginal: Papon gets more respect from me because he tries to bring Assamese traditional and folk songs to national stage. Arijit, Kumar Shanu, Abhijeet, none did this. They come/came to bengal to sing bengali songs, but that's it.
